{"type": "article", "id": 50843, "title": "指南一： Hey girls，周末不浪，还叫周末？", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 269276, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "<p><style> @font-face{ font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"宋体\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"Calibri\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"微软雅黑\"; }  p.MsoNormal{ mso-style-name:正文; mso-style-parent:\"\"; margin:0pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; mso-pagination:none; text-align:justify; text-justify:inter-ideograph; font-family:Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; }  span.msoIns{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:underline; text-underline:single; color:blue; }  span.msoDel{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:line-through; color:red; } @page{mso-page-border-surround-header:no; \tmso-page-border-surround-footer:no;}@page Section0{ } div.Section0{page:Section0;}</style></p><p>厌倦了都市生活的浮躁与快节奏，所有人都会期待能够放下手中的一切，去诗和远方，看山看海，看星星看月亮，总之，就是做一些让人身心愉悦的事情。</p><p>虽然现实总是如此的残酷，完全逃离钢筋水泥几乎不可能，但趁着周末约着两三好友或是恋爱伴侣出去逛吃逛吃还是触手可及的。在精致的美食间和聊不尽的gossip中，悠闲放松的时光被拉得足够长。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306112749NWPGAiCkcvT4h6uQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562061\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><style> @font-face{ font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"宋体\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"Calibri\"; }  @font-face{ font-family:\"微软雅黑\"; }  p.MsoNormal{ mso-style-name:正文; mso-style-parent:\"\"; margin:0pt; margin-bottom:.0001pt; mso-pagination:none; text-align:justify; text-justify:inter-ideograph; font-family:Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; }  span.msoIns{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:underline; text-underline:single; color:blue; }  span.msoDel{ mso-style-type:export-only; mso-style-name:\"\"; text-decoration:line-through; color:red; } @page{mso-page-border-surround-header:no; \tmso-page-border-surround-footer:no;}@page Section0{ } div.Section0{page:Section0;}</style></p><p><font face=\"微软雅黑\">但现实问题是，有不少</font>girls到了周六早上才认真思考起来：平常没有好好护理，皮肤干到没法出镜发朋友圈怎么办？外面<font face=\"微软雅黑\">太阳看着好大，要不要出门，但这个</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">周末就这么又丧了？喂，</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">周末</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">不出去浪，你和周末有仇吗？</font></p><h3><b><b>都市约会“小白瓶”，尽情去享受阳光吧！</b></b></h3><p><font face=\"微软雅黑\">你忽然想起新入手的神器</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">，似乎能解决所有的后顾之忧，它</font><font face=\"微软雅黑\">正在梳妆台上等你</font>“宠幸”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306112820YBlpnkvzXVrIwEs3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500060\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这支“约会神器”——<a href=\"http://m.sisley.com.cn/daily-defense-spf50.html?utm_source=Qdaily&amp;utm_medium=display&amp;utm_term=PB&amp;utm_campaign=PB%5F2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">法国希思黎焕白日间防护乳</a>质感盈透，柔若羽翼，奢润的乳液质地，一抹宛如轻纱萦绕，流动性极佳。轻轻推开后清新细滑，跟“黏腻”完全不挨边。这款时尚小白瓶能给你8小时全天候保护，无与伦比的水润质地让你似乎被“保湿面霜”所包围。而独有的焕白晶萃复合专利配方，直击黑斑生成的根源，高效淡化色斑，与所有的斑点say goodbye！</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180306112836wpdHRBaDybGzWgx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500060\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美白、滋润双管齐下，让你尽情享受周末，享受阳光，享受与男友和闺蜜relax的美妙时光。说不定，你还不由自主安利给他们呢！<br></p>"}